Skill.SkillDesc:
Enters [Funeral Rite] state. If Lady Nifle's Skill Range exceeds 100%, converts the excess portion into Skill Damage at a certain percentage, and the Skill Range will be reduced to and remain at 100% until the [Funeral Rite] state ends.

While in [Funeral Rite] state:
Increases Lady Nifle's Ranged Weapon Trigger Probability;
Does not consume Sanity when summoning [Solar Eclipse] and increases the damage dealt by [Solar Eclipse];
Does not consume Sanity when summoning [Lunar Hunt] and pulls all targets on hit towards the center.

The [Funeral Rite] state ends after a certain period of time or after summoning [Lunar Hunt] and [Solar Eclipse] 6 times.
